messages.title: 3 POSITIVE REASONS TO VOTE FOR GRAHAM STUART
messages.content: Working hard: Graham has been one of the hardest working MPs - from street surgeries to local campaigns no one has done more. Working hard: Graham has been an active MP in Parliament - speaking frequently on many local issues. Working hard: Graham gets things done, from community hospitals, the Beverley bypass and championing local schools, Graham has been tireless in working for the constituency.
